StartingMessage:
	'''
	Welcome to [c/77ffb9:Critical Strikes Overhaul]!
	FYI, this mod increases boss HP by 30% by default for balancing purposes; you can undo this change via the configm
	If you have any questions or feedback on how the mod functions, feel free to ask on the Discord server, linked on the workshop
	Have fun!
	'''
sawDamageReduced: -Chainsaw damage greatly reduced by this critical strike condition
overclockedTooltip: Overclocked: Greater than max number of augmentations causes you to take damage upon use
